The exact same title `🔴CUSTOM ROOM | 1v1 TDM | FACECAM 😍 | BGMI LIVE WITH AIS...` was used 3 times. This is a major SEO problem:
- YouTube treats repeated titles as low-effort signal → throttles distribution
- Returning viewers can''t tell which video they already watched → click-through drops
- The lowest performer (May 4 — 439 views) is half the median. **This is exactly the algorithmic-suppression signal the performance-review workflow is built for.**

