- **Description hook (reverent voice):** "अधिक मास का प्रारंभ हो रहा है — भगवान विष्णु का सबसे प्रिय मास। इस पुण्य अवसर पर सुनिए यह भक्ति-रस से भरा बहुप्रिय भजन। 🙏 ॐ नमो नारायणाय।"
- **Tags:** Adhik Maas 2026, Purushottam Maas, Adhik Maas bhajan, Vishnu bhajan, Shri Vishnu, Om Namo Narayanaya, Vishnu mantra, devotional song, Bhakti Sangeet, Kundan Parashar, Hindi bhajan, Adhik Jyeshtha 2026, Mal Maas (≤500 chars total).
- **Thumbnail prompt (nano_banana_2, 3-variant default):** "Serene image of Lord Vishnu seated on Sheshnag with Lakshmi at his feet, soft golden divine light, lotus pond foreground, cream/saffron background gradient. Bold Devanagari title ''अधिक मास'' in deep gold (#D4AF37) at top, sub-text ''पुरुषोत्तम मास'' in saffron (#E85002) below. Calm composition — no diagonal/shouty elements. Subtle floral border. 1280×720." — generate 3 variants with deity composition variations.

#### Idea S2 — "Om Namo Bhagavate Vasudevaya 108 Times" recitation (P0 — Pillar-3 long-form)
- **Format:** Long-form 30-45 min mantra-jaap, single Krishna/Vishnu image, mantra count display in lower-third. Pillar-3 monthly-cadence anchor — Adhik Maas is THE month for this.
- **Theme:** The 12-syllable Vishnu mantra recited 108 times. Background-listening hours = phenomenal watch-time per Audience-Asks-2 + 3 in learnings (viewers want long-form for jaap-along).
- **Title (Devanagari + Roman):** "ॐ नमो भगवते वासुदेवाय — 108 बार | Vishnu Mantra Jaap | Adhik Maas Special | Kundan Parashar"
- **Voice-over hook (calm, opening):** "अधिक मास के पुण्य अवसर पर, भगवान विष्णु के द्वादशाक्षर मंत्र का 108 बार जाप। आइए मिलकर साधना करें।"
- **Thumbnail prompt:** "Lord Krishna in meditation pose, peacock-feather crown detail, soft lotus and tulsi-leaf floral border. Deep blue (#1A2E5C) temple-arch background gradient. ''ॐ नमो भगवते वासुदेवाय'' in Tiro Devanagari Hindi at heavy weight, deep gold. Sub-text ''108 बार · अधिक मास'' in saffron. 1280×720, 3-variant default."
- **Description-tags add-on:** "Adhik Maas mantra jaap, Vishnu 108 times, Om Namo Bhagavate Vasudevaya, Vishnu mantra long form, peaceful chanting, Adhik Maas 2026 Vishesh."

#### Idea S3 — Daily Adhik Maas Shorts series (Pillar-2 ramp-up + closes the 0-Shorts gap)
- **Format:** 30-45s vertical Shorts, 1 per day for 30 days (or condensed 5/week). Each short = 1 Vishnu naam from the 108 names, Devanagari, calm voice-over, deity-image static.
- **Why this idea:** Closes the **zero-Shorts-in-30d** gap flagged in today''s daily research; rides the same morning-Shiv-Shorts format that''s working for T-Series Bhakti Sagar at 7.33× their median (now applied to Vishnu/Krishna for Adhik Maas).
- **Series title pattern (Devanagari):** "विष्णु सहस्रनाम — दिन [N]: [नाम] | Adhik Maas Series"
  - Example Day-1: "विष्णु सहस्रनाम — दिन 1: ॐ विश्वम् | Adhik Maas Series · Kundan Parashar"
- **Voice-over hook (per Short):** Single Vishnu naam announced in clear Sanskrit, brief 1-line meaning in Hindi, ''Om Namo Narayanaya'' jaap closer. Reverent, peaceful, no clickbait.
- **IG Reel mirror:** Same vertical asset cross-posted to IG (once instagram.md is set up — flagged in this same daily research). Caption: "अधिक मास के 30 दिन — विष्णु सहस्रनाम का प्रवाह। आज का नाम: [नाम]। 🙏 #AdhikMaas2026 #PurushottamMaas #VishnuBhajan"
- **Community-post poll:** "अधिक मास में आप किस रूप में भगवान विष्णु का स्मरण करते हैं? 1) श्री कृष्ण  2) श्री राम  3) नारायण  4) पुरुषोत्तम" — drives discussion within Pillar-1 audience.
- **Tags (per Short):** Adhik Maas, Purushottam Maas, Vishnu Sahasranam, Vishnu naam, Adhik Maas Shorts, Bhakti Shorts, Kundan Parashar (≤500 chars, event-anchored).

### Action items
- [ ] **Notify Kundan in chat today (Sat May 9):** "Adhik Maas opens May 17 — 30-day Vishnu/Krishna content window. Need at minimum: 1 opening Vishnu bhajan (S1) staged for Fri May 15 publish, 1 Vishnu mantra 108-times long-form (S2) for Sat May 16 publish, and S3 daily-Shorts series ideally beginning May 17."
- [ ] **Confirm asset readiness:** Check Kundan''s swipe-file for any existing Vishnu/Krishna bhajan recordings or Vishnu-mantra long-form audio that could be repurposed under Adhik-Maas framing without new recording — this is the 8-day prep runway, much tighter than ideal for original recording.
- [ ] **Stream-day asset pack (optional):** if Kundan is open to a live Adhik-Maas opening kirtan stream (May 17 evening), ask in chat *"Prep stream-day pack for kundan-parashar — Adhik Maas opening kirtan, going live evening May 17"*.
- [ ] **Reflect into competitors.json (next daily run):** add T-Series Bhakti Sagar''s Adhik Maas releases when they appear (likely starting ~May 14-15) — they''ll publish first, useful as keyword/SEO benchmark.
- [ ] **Pillar-3 cadence shift:** today''s daily research says Pillar-3 is 1/month — recommend bumping to weekly during Adhik Maas (4 long-form 30-60 min mantra jaap pieces in 30 days), since Adhik Maas IS the month built for jaap audiences.
- [ ] **Apply DO/NEVER from brand-kit:** every asset stays reverent + Sanskrit-accurate · NO supernatural-outcome claims (e.g., "Adhik Maas mein yeh sun lo, har manokamna poori") — this is an algorithmic flag risk per content-strategy.md negative keywords. Frame benefits in shraddha / shanti / anand / mukti language only.

', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);

